<h2>Berlin - Madrid (Sammelband)</h2>
<h3>Postdiktatoriale Großstadtliteratur</h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='736'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
